parameters.query:
SELECT 
  sr.response_id,
  sr.submitted_at,
  sr.feedback_text,
  sr.ai_category,
  sr.sentiment_score,
  sr.sentiment_label,
  ji.jira_issue_key,
  ji.issue_status,
  ji.created_date as jira_created
FROM survey_responses sr
